---
description: Enforced observability specialist routing
alwaysApply: false
globs:
  - "**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}"
  - "**/*log*"
  - "**/*trace*"
  - "**/*metric*"
  - "**/*audit*"
  - "**/*job*"
  - "**/*queue*"
---

If task intent or touched files indicate observability-sensitive scope (logging, tracing, auditability, metrics, retries, jobs), `observability-agent` is required for L2+ work.

If task intent is primarily recurring-failure or churn analysis from logs, `log-analyst-agent` is required.
